title: Seychelles  CPI Housing Utilities
description: CPI Housing Utilities in Seychelles decreased to 145.34 points in October from 145.42 points in September of 2022. CPI Housing Utilities in Seychelles averaged 96.86 points from 2007 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 145.65 points in August of 2022 and a record low of 44.14 points in February of 2007. This page provides - Seychelles  Cpi Housing Utilities- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: National Bureau of Statistics, Seychelles
